textBox.richText: I died... In a Hollywood hotel

http://splatinum.bandcamp.com/ Yesterday I recorded vocals for a dubstep remix Splatinum is doing. I think it might turn out to be the coolest shit I have ever heard. Big ups, my men. Today I am recording with Cozmic Danger. I am so excited to hear how their new tracks are coming along. It’s the dirtiest house I have ever heard. As their homegirl Lindsey Fish said, so dirty it makes you want to go and wipe down their records. LOVE IT
